data.description: Looking for a beautiful home with 2 Master Bedrooms and 1 Acre Lot? Look no more! Come take a look at this amazing home featuring laminate and tile flooring throughout, large split floorplan, formal dining room as well as breakfast nook in the kitchen. This home also features a 3 car garage, gazebo, enclosed patio storage unit, mature landscaping, horseshoe driveway, and RV parking. Home is centrally located in the heart of Hesperia, commuter friendly, near schools, parks and shopping.
